## 3.8 Instrumentation (Switch)
Track:
- Switch Kit opens
- Switch confirmed
- Switch cancelled before start
- Switch activated
- Time from confirm → active
- % of PROVIDER-covered categories that convert to switches
- Retention impact of switches (later)

