## 6) Opinionated Notes (to make 3D excellent)

### Switch Kit
- Make start date selection default to **next cycle** (low chaos).
- Keep it premium: “We’ll take it from here.”
- Never surprise-charge. Always next-cycle adjustments.
- Don’t ask for vendor info. That’s not needed and adds friction.

### Ops Cockpit
- Keep it brutally simple. Operators need decisions, not charts.
- Use drilldowns instead of overbuilt dashboards.
- Make every KPI clickable to the underlying jobs/properties/providers.
- Focus on keeping support cost low: proof + issues matter most.

